### Rust (Cargo, rustc, maturin, PyO3) ###
# This project commits `Cargo.lock`; keep it out of any broad ignore rules below.
# Primary build tree (workspace root). Do not commit compiled crates or incremental state.
/target/
/debug/

# Static and link artifacts sometimes produced at repo root by bad invocations or local experiments
*.rlib
/*.o
/*.obj
/*.a
*.exp
*.ilk

# rustfmt
**/*.rs.bk

# MSVC debug symbols
*.pdb

# macOS debug bundles from `cargo build` / Instruments
**/*.dSYM/

